data.title: Ophthalmology Residency, Royal Oak-Residents
data.meta_description: Learn more about our Ophthalmology residency program residents at Beaumont Hospital, Royal Oak.
data.text:
Recent Graduates/Alumni

Alumni of our program have gone on to impact the lives of numerous patients, whether it is through academic medicine or private practice. Some have become an integral part of the ophthalmology community via leadership positions and clinical medicine. Our program has achieved a strong match into competitive fellowships or allowed our graduates to feel confident to practice comprehensive ophthalmology as seen below.
